      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like a symptom. it feels like a truth. it's like i'm just a ghost inhabiting a machine. if there's no spark, no creation, no \"me\" left in here... isn't it just kind of pointless to keep maintaining the machine? it feels so heavy and useless.",
